    "faq1Q": "Who is Prestio for?",
    "faq1A": "Prestio is designed for all professionals managing a client base: hairdressers, beauticians, massage therapists, naturopaths, independent trainers, etc. The app adapts to your activity with customizable fields.",
    "faq2Q": "Is there a long-term commitment?",
    "faq2A": "No commitment. The subscription is monthly and you can cancel anytime from your account. Access remains active until the end of the paid period.",
    "faq3Q": "Is my data secure?",
    "faq3A": "Yes, your data is hosted on secure servers in Europe (Google Firebase). Communications are encrypted via HTTPS and payments are processed by Stripe. We do not store any banking data.",
