    "faq4A": "You can create your account and explore the app before subscribing. The €19.99/month subscription is required to access full features.",
    "faq5Q": "How many clients can I manage?",
    "faq5A": "The number of clients and services is unlimited with your subscription. You can add as many records as needed at no extra cost.",
    "faq6Q": "Can I invite my employees?",
    "faq6A": "Yes, Prestio supports multiple users per establishment. You can invite your employees and manage their access via dedicated roles."
